sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as p67 CLI
    participant CD as controld
    participant RA as Runtime Adapter<br/>(Docker or SPCS)
    participant RUN as p67-runner
    participant SF as Snowflake
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    CLI->>CD: POST /api/workflow/:id/run
    CD->>DB: Create WorkflowRun (status=Running)
    CD-->>CLI: 202 { runId, status: "running" }

    Note over CD: Background execution begins

    CD->>CD: Parse manifest.yaml<br/>Hydrate config (secrets, OAuth tokens)
    CD->>RA: Spawn runner container

    alt Docker (local)
        RA->>RUN: docker run -i -v /workflow:ro
    else SPCS (production)
        RA->>SF: Upload workflow to stage
        RA->>RUN: EXECUTE JOB SERVICE<br/>(inline spec YAML)
    end

    Note over CD,RUN: NDJSON IPC over stdin/stdout

    CD->>RUN: RunWorkflow message<br/>(config, params, credentials)
    RUN->>RUN: Load index.js/main.py<br/>Call main(sdk)

    loop Workflow execution
        RUN->>SF: SDK calls (SQL, Cortex, HTTP...)
        SF-->>RUN: Results
    end

    RUN-->>CD: { type: "result", data: ... }
    CD->>DB: Update WorkflowRun<br/>(status=Completed, result)

    loop Polling
        CLI->>CD: GET /api/workflow/runs/:runId
        CD-->>CLI: { status, result }
    end
